issue.title: Enable -Wshadow by default
issue.body:
Test and enabled `-Wshadow` by default, add developer note about this change (see #8105).

As my native language is not English, I'm open to suggestions.

[Edits from maintainers allowed for easier cooperation.]

issue.title: [port] bring src/univalue up to core/master
issue.body:
3 commits that bring this 3rd-party library up to core/master.  The real change is the first one with UTF-8 support; the rest is cosmetic.

bitcoin#7892   Add full UTF-8 support to RPC
bitcoin#8807
bitcoin#8863

issue.title: Update univalue subtree
issue.body: This removes the deprecated `std::pair` wrappers from univalue, so that they are not accidentally re-introduced in our code base.
